---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";

const title = "Disclaimer | Daily Life Hacks";
const description = "Medical and Nutrition Disclaimer for Daily Life Hacks.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
    <Header />
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 prose prose-lg">
        <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
        <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

        <div
            class="p-6 my-8 rounded-r-lg"
            style="background-color: var(--input-bg); border-left: 4px solid #F29B30;"
        >
            <p
                class="font-bold text-lg mb-2"
                style="color: var(--heading-color);"
            >
                Important Notice
            </p>
            <p class="italic" style="color: var(--text-color);">
                The information on this site is not intended or implied to be a
                substitute for professional financial and/or medical advice. All
                content, including text, graphics, images and information,
                contained on or available through this web site is for general
                information purposes only. The information and materials
                contained in these pages and the terms, conditions and
                descriptions that appear, are subject to change without notice.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h2>1. General Information</h2>
        <p>
            The content provided on Daily Life Hacks is for informational and
            educational purposes only. It is not intended to be a substitute for
            professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. We do not
            provide diagnoses, treatments, or medical services.
        </p>

        <h2>2. No Doctor-Patient Relationship</h2>
        <p>
            Accessing or using this website does not create a doctor-patient or
            professional-client relationship between you and Daily Life Hacks or
            its authors. The authors of this website are not licensed medical
            professionals, and the information shared is based on personal
            research, experience, or general knowledge.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Medical Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
            Always seek the advice of your physician, registered dietitian, or
            other qualified health provider with any questions you may have
            regarding a medical condition, dietary changes, or supplement use.
            Never disregard professional medical advice or delay in seeking it
            because of something you have read on this website.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you think you may have a medical emergency, call your doctor or
            emergency services immediately. Reliance on any information provided
            by Daily Life Hacks is solely at your own risk.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Financial Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
            The financial information provided on Daily Life Hacks is for
            informational and educational purposes only and does not constitute
            financial advice, investment advice, trading advice, or any other
            type of advice. We are not financial advisors.
        </p>
        <p>
            You should not make any financial decisions based solely on the
            information presented here without consulting a qualified financial
            professional who is aware of your specific financial situation.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <p>
            Some of the links on this website may be "affiliate links." This
            means if you click on the link and purchase an item, Daily Life
            Hacks may receive an affiliate commission. This comes at no extra
            cost to you. We disclose this in accordance with the Federal Trade
            Commission's guidelines.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Errors and Omissions</h2>
        <p>
            While we strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information, the
            fields of nutrition, medicine, and finance are constantly evolving.
            We cannot guarantee that all information on this website is
            complete, accurate, or current. We are not responsible for any
            errors or omissions, or for the results obtained from the use of
            this information.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
            By using this website, you agree to absolve Daily Life Hacks of any
            liability or loss that you or any other person may incur from use of
            the information, products, or materials that you request or receive
            through or on our website.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Consent</h2>
        <p>
            By using our website, you hereby consent to our disclaimer and agree
            to its terms.
        </p>
    </div>
    <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
